msgctxt "dn8:1.1"
msgid "Dīgha Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Long Discourses 8"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "dn8:2.1"
msgid "Mahāsīhanādasutta"
msgstr "The Longer Discourse on the Lion’s Roar"

#. </h1></div><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="wp" id="wp1"></a><a
#. class="pts" id="pts1.161"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:3.1"
msgid "<span class=\"evam\">Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​</span>"
msgstr "<span class=”evam”>So I have heard.</span>"

#. VAR: uruññāyaṃ → ujuññāyaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn8:3.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā uruññāyaṃ viharati kaṇṇakatthale migadāye."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Ujuñña, in the deer park at "
"Kaṇṇakatthala."

msgctxt "dn8:3.3"
msgid "Atha kho acelo kassapo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami;"
msgstr "Then the naked ascetic Kassapa went up to the Buddha"

msgctxt "dn8:3.4"
msgid "upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi."
msgstr "and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "dn8:3.5"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he stood to one side,"

msgctxt "dn8:3.6"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho acelo kassapo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "dn8:3.7"
msgid "“<a class=\"wp\" id=\"wp2\"></a> sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama:"
msgstr "“Master Gotama, I have heard the following:"

# See AN 10.94
msgctxt "dn8:3.8"
msgid ""
"‘samaṇo gotamo sabbaṃ tapaṃ garahati, sabbaṃ tapassiṃ lūkhājīviṃ ekaṃsena "
"upakkosati upavadatī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The ascetic Gotama criticizes all forms of mortification. He categorically "
"condemns and denounces those self-mortifiers who live rough.’"

msgctxt "dn8:3.9"
msgid "Ye te, bho gotama, evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr "Do those who say this "

#. VAR: vādānuvādo → vādānupāto (^sn12.24#1 [24. Añña­titthi­ya­sutta])
msgctxt "dn8:3.10"
msgid ""
"‘samaṇo gotamo sabbaṃ tapaṃ garahati, sabbaṃ tapassiṃ lūkhājīviṃ ekaṃsena "
"upakkosati upavadatī’ti, kacci te bhoto gotamassa vuttavādino, na ca "
"bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhanti, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākaronti, "
"na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānuvādo gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchati?"
msgstr ""
"repeat what the Buddha has said, and not misrepresent him with an untruth? "
"Is their explanation in line with the teaching? Are there any legitimate "
"grounds for rebuke and criticism?"

msgctxt "dn8:3.11"
msgid "Anabbhakkhātukāmā hi mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotaman”ti."
msgstr "For we don’t want to misrepresent Master Gotama.”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="wp" id="wp3"></a><a class="pts"
#. id="pts1.162"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:4.1"
msgid "“Ye te, kassapa, evamāhaṃsu:"
msgstr "“Kassapa, those who say this"

msgctxt "dn8:4.2"
msgid ""
"‘samaṇo gotamo sabbaṃ tapaṃ garahati, sabbaṃ tapassiṃ lūkhājīviṃ ekaṃsena "
"upakkosati upavadatī’ti, na me te vuttavādino, abbhācikkhanti ca pana maṃ te "
"asatā abhūtena."
msgstr ""
"do not repeat what I have said. They misrepresent me with what is false, "
"baseless, and untrue."

msgctxt "dn8:4.3"
msgid ""
"Idhāhaṃ, kassapa, ekaccaṃ tapassiṃ lūkhājīviṃ passāmi dibbena cakkhunā "
"visuddhena atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ "
"vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ."
msgstr ""
"With clairvoyance that is purified and superhuman, I see some self-mortifier "
"who lives rough reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "dn8:4.4"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, kassapa, ekaccaṃ tapassiṃ lūkhājīviṃ passāmi dibbena cakkhunā "
"visuddhena atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ "
"lokaṃ upapannaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But I see another self-mortifier who lives rough reborn in a good place, a "
"heavenly realm."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:5.1"
msgid ""
"Idhāhaṃ, kassapa, ekaccaṃ tapassiṃ appadukkhavihāriṃ passāmi dibbena "
"cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ "
"duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannaṃ."
msgstr "I see some self-mortifier who takes it easy reborn in a place of loss."

msgctxt "dn8:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha panāhaṃ, kassapa, ekaccaṃ tapassiṃ appadukkhavihāriṃ passāmi dibbena "
"cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ "
"saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But I see another self-mortifier who takes it easy reborn in a good place, a "
"heavenly realm."

msgctxt "dn8:5.3"
msgid ""
"Yohaṃ, kassapa, imesaṃ tapassīnaṃ evaṃ āgatiñca gatiñca cutiñca upapattiñca "
"yathābhūtaṃ pajānāmi, sohaṃ kiṃ sabbaṃ tapaṃ garahissāmi, sabbaṃ vā tapassiṃ "
"lūkhājīviṃ ekaṃsena upakkosissāmi upavadissāmi?"
msgstr ""
"Since I truly understand the coming and going, dying and rebirth of these "
"self-mortifiers in this way, how could I criticize all forms of "
"mortification, or categorically condemn and denounce those self-mortifiers "
"who live rough?"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="wp" id="wp4"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:6.1"
msgid ""
"Santi, kassapa, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā paṇḍitā nipuṇā kataparappavādā "
"vālavedhirūpā."
msgstr ""
"There are some clever ascetics and brahmins who are subtle, accomplished in "
"the doctrines of others, hair-splitters. You’d think they live to demolish "
"convictions with their intellect. "

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn8:6.2"
msgid "Te bhindantā maññe caranti paññāgatena diṭṭhigatāni."
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn8:6.3"
msgid "Tehipi me saddhiṃ ekaccesu ṭhānesu sameti, ekaccesu ṭhānesu na sameti."
msgstr "They agree with me in some matters and disagree in others."

msgctxt "dn8:6.4"
msgid "Yaṃ te ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘sādhū’ti, mayampi taṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘sādhū’ti."
msgstr "Some of the things that they applaud, I also applaud."

msgctxt "dn8:6.5"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ te ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘na sādhū’ti, mayampi taṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘na sādhū’ti."
msgstr "Some of the things that they don’t applaud, I also don’t applaud."

msgctxt "dn8:6.6"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ te ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘sādhū’ti, mayaṃ taṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘na sādhū’ti."
msgstr "But some of the things that they applaud, I don’t applaud."

msgctxt "dn8:6.7"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ te ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘na sādhū’ti, mayaṃ taṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘sādhū’ti."
msgstr "And some of the things that they don’t applaud, I do applaud."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="pts" id="pts1.163"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:7.1"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ mayaṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘sādhū’ti, parepi taṃ ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘sādhū’ti."
msgstr "Some of the things that I applaud, others also applaud."

msgctxt "dn8:7.2"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ mayaṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘na sādhū’ti, parepi taṃ ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘na "
"sādhū’ti."
msgstr "Some of the things that I don’t applaud, they also don’t applaud."

msgctxt "dn8:7.3"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ mayaṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘na sādhū’ti, pare taṃ ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘sādhū’ti."
msgstr "But some of the things that I don’t applaud, others do applaud."

msgctxt "dn8:7.4"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ mayaṃ ekaccaṃ vadema ‘sādhū’ti, pare taṃ ekaccaṃ vadanti ‘na sādhū’ti."
msgstr "And some of the things that I do applaud, others don’t applaud."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn8:8.1"
msgid "1. Samanuyuñjāpanakathā"
msgstr "Examination"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="wp" id="wp5"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:9.1"
msgid "Tyāhaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evaṃ vadāmi:"
msgstr "I go up to them and say:"

msgctxt "dn8:9.2"
msgid "‘yesu no, āvuso, ṭhānesu na sameti, tiṭṭhantu tāni ṭhānāni."
msgstr "‘Let us leave aside those matters on which we disagree."

msgctxt "dn8:9.3"
msgid ""
"Yesu ṭhānesu sameti, tattha viññū samanuyuñjantaṃ samanugāhantaṃ "
"samanubhāsantaṃ satthārā vā satthāraṃ saṅghena vā saṅghaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"But there are some matters on which we agree. Regarding these, sensible "
"people, questioning, pressing, and examining, would compare teacher with "
"teacher or community with community:"

msgctxt "dn8:9.4"
msgid ""
"“ye imesaṃ bhavataṃ dhammā akusalā akusalasaṅkhātā, sāvajjā sāvajjasaṅkhātā, "
"asevitabbā asevitabbasaṅkhātā, na alamariyā na alamariyasaṅkhātā, kaṇhā "
"kaṇhasaṅkhātā."
msgstr ""
"“There are things that are unskillful, blameworthy, not to be cultivated, "
"unworthy of the noble ones, and dark—and are reckoned as such."

msgctxt "dn8:9.5"
msgid ""
"Ko ime dhamme anavasesaṃ pahāya vattati, samaṇo vā gotamo, pare vā pana "
"bhonto gaṇācariyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Who behaves like they’ve totally given these things up: the ascetic Gotama, "
"or the teachers of other communities?”’"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="wp" id="wp6"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:10.1"
msgid ""
"Ṭhānaṃ kho panetaṃ, kassapa, vijjati, yaṃ viññū samanuyuñjantā samanugāhantā "
"samanubhāsantā evaṃ vadeyyuṃ:"
msgstr "It’s possible that they might say:"

msgctxt "dn8:10.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye imesaṃ bhavataṃ dhammā akusalā akusalasaṅkhātā, sāvajjā sāvajjasaṅkhātā, "
"asevitabbā asevitabbasaṅkhātā, na alamariyā na alamariyasaṅkhātā, kaṇhā "
"kaṇhasaṅkhātā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn8:10.3"
msgid ""
"Samaṇo gotamo ime dhamme anavasesaṃ pahāya vattati, yaṃ vā pana bhonto pare "
"gaṇācariyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘The ascetic Gotama behaves like he’s totally given those unskillful things "
"up, compared with the teachers of other communities.’"

msgctxt "dn8:10.4"
msgid ""
"Itiha, kassapa, viññū samanuyuñjantā samanugāhantā samanubhāsantā amheva "
"tattha yebhuyyena pasaṃseyyuṃ."
msgstr ""
"And that’s how, when sensible people examine the matter, they will mostly "
"praise us."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="wp" id="wp7"></a>
msgctxt "dn8:11.1"
msgid ""
"Aparampi no, kassapa, viññū samanuyuñjantaṃ samanugāhantaṃ samanubhāsantaṃ "
"satthārā vā satthāraṃ saṅghena vā saṅghaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"In addition, sensible people, questioning, pressing, and examining, would "
"compare teacher with teacher or community with community:"

msgctxt "dn8:11.2"
msgid ""
"‘ye imesaṃ bhavataṃ dhammā kusalā kusalasaṅkhātā, anavajjā anavajjasaṅkhātā, "
"sevitabbā sevitabbasaṅkhātā, alamariyā alamariyasaṅkhātā, sukkā "
"sukkasaṅkhātā."
msgstr ""
"‘There are things that are skillful, blameless, worth cultivating, worthy of "
"the noble ones, and bright—and are reckoned as such."

msgctxt "dn8:11.3"
msgid ""
"Ko ime dhamme anavasesaṃ samādāya vattati, samaṇo vā gotamo, pare vā pana "
"bhonto gaṇācariyā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"Who proceeds having totally undertaken these things: the ascetic Gotama, or "
"the teachers of other communities?’"

